# Deal 1: Prisoner's Dilemma (No Communication)    Merrill Flood, Melvin Dresher, Albert W. Tucker
                         Person A
                         -----------------------------------------
                         Betray                 Silence
                         -----------------------------------------
Person B | Betray        each serves 2 years    A=free, B=3 years
         | Silence       A=3 years, B=free      Each serves 1 year

